{"tid":2237250,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"如果政府唔做第3期保就業，對大家份工有無影響？","createTime":"2020-10-10T06:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T04:56:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"11aa1f544236e0d86343f42b9f366c4f821d81b5","tid":2237250,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">若不推第三輪保就業 部分企業或結業</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2593141/郭振華%3A若不推第三輪保就業+部分企業或結業\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2593141%2F%E9%83%AD%E6%8C%AF%E8%8F%AF%253A%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%A8%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E8%BC%AA%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%2B%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E6%88%96%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=6b6f02cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2593141/郭振華%3A若不推第三輪保就業+部分企業或結業</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/09/27/2593141_617068968014bf87b16cf05c5845317a_320.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2F2593141_617068968014bf87b16cf05c5845317a_320.png&h=ab8e76e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府早前表示，暫無意推出第三輪「保就業」計劃，勞顧會僱主代表郭振華表示，部分企業或結業。<br />\n<br />\n郭振華出席無綫節目《講清講楚》時表示，如果兩輪「保就業」計劃能發動勞資雙方的新智慧，在疫情下能繼續經營的模式，這些企業會繼續經營下去。但如果經過這兩輪都不能逆轉，亦無辦法可支援企業繼續經營下去，而政府沒有推出第三輪「保就業」計劃，並且疫情持續下，相信結業情況會較嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，受疫情影響，預料本港飲食業及零售市道即使到農曆新年都不會有明顯好轉。他稱，在過年時，一般飲食業、零售業等都是旺季，但如果疫情影響，「限聚令」仍然存在，相信大家都會預測到這些消費不會多。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，若凍結最低工資水平，帶出的訊息是經濟不穩、企業信心差，即使調高最低工資水平，對勞動市場幫助不大，企業在經營困境下，或有更大機會要求工作能力較弱的低收入人士放無薪假。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無影響，有實力唔怕！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能會失業 / 減薪"},{"pid":"16eaceefb027746819f6f4d7cb7d07ea11ef207f","tid":2237250,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"保就業又咪益商家佬"},{"pid":"1ef22de8fdb46432320f321ac5ba05eeffe6b3fe","tid":2237250,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"efd5b9075ab6fae65e113deca738aa929b3d5ef0","tid":2237250,"uid":322130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"政府益商界...市民生活理撚"},{"pid":"67d2cfb12937fcdae4d03a33e07fb6c2fc745478","tid":2237250,"uid":242921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"廢人先要等政府救濟。 <br />\n<br />\n利申：做sales,  賣醫療產品十幾年，年薪過百萬。"},{"pid":"6467c21c9d205818699cf39e01fab70a4040e9f2","tid":2237250,"uid":367814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d2cfb12937fcdae4d03a33e07fb6c2fc745478","tid":2237250,"uid":242921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"廢人先要等政府救濟。 <br />\n<br />\n利申：做sales,  賣醫療產品十幾年，年薪過百萬。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"厲害，心藏科？"}]}